2:T72a,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"Is Kapwing AI better than Pika?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"It depends on your needs. Kapwing AI scores 6.0 overall while Pika scores 7.0. Kapwing AI is best for content teams collaborating on video and quick social media edits, while Pika excels for social media content creators and quick AI video generation."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which is cheaper, Kapwing AI or Pika?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Kapwing AI starts at $16/mo and Pika starts at $8/mo. Kapwing AI offers a free plan. Pika offers a free plan. Overall value depends on which features you need."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can I switch from Kapwing AI to Pika?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes, most users can migrate between these platforms. Both Kapwing AI and Pika support data import/export. The migration process typically involves exporting your data from one platform and importing it into the other. Some tools also offer migration assistance to make the transition smoother."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What do users say about Kapwing AI vs Pika?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"On review platforms, Kapwing AI holds an overall rating of 6/10 and an ease of use score of 8/10. Pika has an overall rating of 7/10 and ease of use score of 9/10. Users praise Kapwing AI for browser-based, no install and Pika for easy to use interface."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which should I choose in 2026, Kapwing AI or Pika?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"In 2026, we recommend Pika for most users based on its overall score and feature set. However, Kapwing AI remains a strong contender, especially if you prioritize browser-based, no install. Try both free trials before committing."}}]}0:{"buildId":"oWPZTPCPUwZMl312gxRMA","rsc":["$","$1","c",{"children":[[["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"$2